      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/d576e47ec29592a74d7f18040459665c_3269229002434222896.png",
                "id": "talent30808",
                "key": "忍刀·終末番",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "忍刀·終末番"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，本角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">準備技能</span>：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">風風輪舞踢</span>。</p><p>如果目前技能引發了擴散，則<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">風風輪舞踢</span>將改為造成被擴散元素的傷害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">風風輪舞踢</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>（需準備1個行動輪）</p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>（或被擴散元素的傷害）。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/0d49f00d17fc351c654b35e9c3df69a0_2300065538523107118.png",
                "id": "talent22236",
                "key": "嗚呼流·風隱急進",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "嗚呼流·風隱急進"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">不倒貉貉</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/9810aeb4be1a04544ed8bd2e2fdb4c9f_6391024862140662275.png",
                "id": "talent40042",
                "key": "嗚呼流·影貉繚亂",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "嗚呼流·影貉繚亂"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，治療我方受傷最多的角色2點。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8486860900881117445.png",
                "id": "talent59795",
                "key": "不倒貉貉",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/48a8c90a05701c12e7e340501f089bc8_8936466309040795378.png",
                "title": "不倒貉貉"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（冰）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（水）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（火）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（雷）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_4426988076419002837.png",
                "id": "talent55789",
                "key": "風元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "風元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備技能</span></p><p>有些技能無法直接使用，而是需要一定次數的行動輪來進行<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>。</p><p>輪到一位牌手行動時，如果該牌手的「出戰角色」正在<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>技能，則跳過該牌手的行動；如果技能已經完成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>，角色將會在此時直接使用此技能。（此類需要<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>的技能，無法觸發「使用技能後」「角色引發元素反應後」等效果。）</p><p>只有「出戰角色」才能<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>技能；如果正在<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>技能的「出戰角色」被切換到後臺，技能的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>就會被打斷。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_4533640607452058011.png",
